{"tid":593840,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"HKTV劇集首登免費電視頻道　4月16日起77台播放","createTime":"2018-03-15T10:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T03:57:43.000Z","uid":26418,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df9875f8e2aff1aa793894dcc33cac54dd812a38","tid":593840,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180315/s00001/1521106927446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180315%2Fs00001%2F1521106927446&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOesVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=966fd7a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180315%2Fs00001%2F1521106927446&h=2d7c95da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180315/s00001/1521106927446</a><br />\n<br />\n有線電視旗下免費電視頻道「奇妙電視 Fantastic TV」，去年5月14日啟播，惟收視和市民關注程度，一直比不上ViuTV和TVB。影視節目評論員游大東在最新一則facebook帖文中，也形容奇妙電視長期「靜過鬼」，惟至近日「總算有點新搞作」，其中一項是4月16日起，在免費電視頻道77台，播出港視製作劇集《來生不做香港人》。<br />\n<br />\n消息最先在有線電視企業旗下網站「<a href=\"http://21126888.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F21126888.com&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOesVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3ffb3e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">21126888.com</a>」曝光，《來生不做香港人》將由4月16日起，逢星期一至五晚8點半，在奇妙電視播放。此劇原由香港電視網絡（HKTV）製作，2014年12月12日起在HKTV網上平台首播，同期在星馬地區付費頻道，以劇名《客家女人》播出。<br />\n<br />\n事隔3年多，港視第二次申請免費電視牌照結果仍是未知數，又已轉型專注經營網購平台，卻有劇集將在免費電視頻道播放。劇情突顯中港矛盾，屬話題之作，游大東在帖文中補充，演員陣容吸引，加上數年前首播已有不錯反應，相信今次登陸77台「應該值得更多觀眾留意和討論」。<br />\n<br />\n對於是次港視劇集登陸奇妙電視，雙方合作協議為何，另外其他港視劇集會否在奇妙電視播放等，本報正向兩家公司查詢。"},{"pid":"18b98a85f93df37470269ff9066f247e64e7723e","tid":593840,"uid":61279,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"播導火新聞線好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2207536d8f607e8e9c77de7b6d773072d53cc02","tid":593840,"uid":26418,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"18b98a85f93df37470269ff9066f247e64e7723e","tid":593840,"uid":61279,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"播導火新聞線好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"你又知佢之後唔會播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n同埋啱啱先開始播 唔好咁心急啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f36bf3260cac645a84eebbc28b6fba08eb4059","tid":593840,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"642f91f7c9d6009c0991d71084995c456802ab22","tid":593840,"uid":26418,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"HKTV好大可能會放棄電視牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW..77台用每秒16Mbps bitrate播港視用靚器材拍嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2cf26b419ecc8a9bb8dbbfa1fb4b17f399a9bf","tid":593840,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6093a111fcd0a4b8c2487c1f6adf17ec1b89e8a","tid":593840,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"642f91f7c9d6009c0991d71084995c456802ab22","tid":593840,"uid":26418,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"HKTV好大可能會放棄電視牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW..77台用每秒16Mbps bitrate播港視用靚器材拍嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/to